reviewText:
Doesn't play on US dvd players.

Doesn't say that anywhere in the description that I see.
MY DVD us blank too ... wtf ??!!  I didn't realize till later because we didn't have the bag set up .. trying to return it ... ugh !!

I purchased this dvd a while back and when I tried playing it found out it was a blank DVD! I have called and emailed te company serveral times since then but have no response.
$29.99 for a Blank dvd is a pretty expensive price.
